{"tid":960230,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加拿大前駐華大使︰必須看清中國的真面目，中國是一個越來越不負責任的大國","createTime":"2018-12-29T08:45:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-29T14:11:31.000Z","uid":39464,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"98433158fa19b50e053617dc765ccb4a5705ddf9","tid":960230,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T08:45:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1435571_1_L_20181229162109.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1435571_1_L_20181229162109.jpg&h=686ae17c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n加拿大前駐華大使馬大維表示，必須看清中國的真面目，批評中國是一個越來越不負責任的大國。<br />\n<br />\n馬大維在09至12年間擔任加拿大駐華大使，他在加拿大環球郵報撰文，表示北京拘押兩名加拿大公民康明凱和斯帕沃爾的做法「殘忍」，但並不罕見，他認為，目前的危機涉及多個層面，包括中國違反伊朗制裁令、利用華為等企業竊取外國技術，以及踐踏本國及外國公民的權利，這些問題匯集一起，令人清楚認識到中國是一個越來越不負責任的大國和夥伴。<br />\n<br />\n馬大維表示，當前的危機為加拿大創造一個展示領導才能的機會，在考慮在與北京打交道時，是否要看中國如何參與基於規則的國際秩序，還是與盟國磋商，以便更好保護敏感技術、更有效地抵禦中國干預民主政治制度，促使中國在國內外尊重人權。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1435571-20181229.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1435571-20181229.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=K8PvC2QKr1Z73RSyGz68H9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=9fcb999a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1435571-20181229.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=f28f917e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1435571-20181229.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"783a028636c6fb800b468d3ebf44c07e9c9ff950","tid":960230,"uid":213877,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T09:01:47.000Z","msg":"好心出兵打啦"},{"pid":"d043599953b48d7451ccdcb988f5018cc451c0c5","tid":960230,"uid":177047,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T09:10:06.000Z","msg":"早十年前佢呢頭吹到自己點樣騰飛的巨龍,果頭講到自己係發展中國家,用呢個行頭避撚哂D環保數,已經夠哂不負責任啦,而家先覺醒?<br />\n而家不過係因為換左個豬頭做國家主席,一野撕爛哂D面具,暗中笑鳩前幾任點解認低威滅自己威風,先顯得特別醜惡咋"},{"pid":"ed550cb4c0003054c483cd41cf0336337226aa7d","tid":960230,"uid":23180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T09:11:53.000Z","msg":"Old news is so...."},{"pid":"722c45083a96ff05c140c2ff5b4d798ecd96ffcf","tid":960230,"uid":24140,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T09:26:55.000Z","msg":"當年SARS已經係啦<br />\n香港再一次走先全人類<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3856cbb185dfc14eee383632cff26750d63c984c","tid":960230,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T09:31:36.000Z","msg":"遲左20年"},{"pid":"cce8d4a42620a8141eaef1ddb45e629e2514935b","tid":960230,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d043599953b48d7451ccdcb988f5018cc451c0c5","tid":960230,"uid":177047,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T09:10:06.000Z","msg":"早十年前佢呢頭吹到自己點樣騰飛的巨龍,果頭講到自己係發展中國家,用呢個行頭避撚哂D環保數,已經夠哂不負責任啦,而家先覺醒?<br />\n而家不過係因為換左個豬頭做國家主席,一野撕爛哂D面具,暗中笑鳩前幾任點解認低威滅自己威風,先顯得特別醜惡咋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T09:33:33.000Z","msg":"希望啲環保撚北上搞走塑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dc6abdfbd146e644f83d9242cdb83c178f77f18","tid":960230,"uid":174420,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T09:35:59.000Z","msg":"又屈我地中國係強國<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4256f8d9cfb408d07c543945317cc74c97a45f3","tid":960230,"uid":25148,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T09:36:15.000Z","msg":"越來越? 乜有負責過<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc572f3b049ac5f96a70e93fd1acc9a778481586","tid":960230,"uid":18569,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"722c45083a96ff05c140c2ff5b4d798ecd96ffcf","tid":960230,"uid":24140,"like":10,